meta_description: The Speedy Pole Tool™ along with the Universal Socket Kit, provides a safe and easy installation for Sammys®, threaded rod, pencil rod, ceiling screws, jack chain, wire and screws.
description: The Speedy Pole Tool™ along with the Universal Socket Kit, provides a safe and easy installation for Sammys®, threaded rod, pencil rod, ceiling screws, jack chain, wire and screws.
short_description: Power the pole with any 3/8" or 1/2" drill. Telescopic design assembles and disassembles for easy transport. Specify desired socket when ordering. Installs eye-lag screws and Sammys for wood and steel from ground level without the need for ladders, scaffolding, or scissor lifts. Increases safety by keeping your employees on the ground. Black anodized aircraft quality aluminum. Designed for standard 12 gauge wire, but will work with up to 8 gauge. Made in USA.

meta_description: The Spot Rite Level provides convenience by functioning as both a torpedo level and gunner nipple all-in-one.  Three airtight vials contain bubble operation and the level is threaded at both ends so you can screw it into a 1/2?, 3/4? or 1? pipe fitting to
description: The Spot Rite Level provides convenience by functioning as both a torpedo level and gunner nipple all-in-one.  Three airtight vials contain bubble operation and the level is threaded at both ends so you can screw it into a 1/2?, 3/4? or 1? pipe fitting to check level, plumb, and 45°. The 3/4” threaded end steps down to ½” while the 1” threads are at the opposite side of the level.   The magnetic base allows for hands-free operation while working with metal applications.
short_description: 3-vial design for measurement of 0° (Level), 45° and 90° (Plumb) angles. Magnetic strip allows for hands-free operation in metal applications. Pocket-sized, lightweight construction is ideal for jobs that have a tight squeeze. Made of tough, impact-resistant plastic. Made in the U.S.A.
